thread.title: Kathleen
thread.title_full: Bake Me A Wish! reviewed by Kathleen

author: Kathleen
title: Kathleen
text: I sent a four cake sampler to my son in Washington, DC for his 24th birthday (I live in Chicago). I know the cakes arrived the morning of his birthday to his home and he reported that they arrive in good condition (a little messed up but still fine). I did not get to taste the cakes so I can't speak to the quality of the cakes but he reported that they were fine.
